msgstr "在 PD 分离场景下，我们提供了一种优化配置。您可以使用以下 shell 脚本分别配置预填充节点和解码节点。"

msgid "### Start Distributed DP Server for prefill-decode disaggregation"
msgstr "### 启动分布式 DP 服务器以实现预填充-解码分离"

msgid ""
"Execute the following Python file on all nodes to use the distributed DP "
"server. (We recommend using this feature on the v0.9.1 official release)"
msgstr "在所有节点上执行以下 Python 文件以使用分布式 DP 服务器。（建议在 v0.9.1 官方版本上使用此功能）"

msgid "=== \"Prefiller node\""
msgstr "=== \"预填充节点\""

msgid "=== \"Decoder node\""
msgstr "=== \"解码节点\""

msgid ""
"Note that the prefiller nodes and the decoder nodes may have different "
"configurations. In this example, each prefiller node is deployed as a master"
" node independently, while the decoder nodes use the 192.0.0.5 node as the "
"master node. This leads to differences in 'dp_size_local' and "
"'dp_rank_start'"
msgstr ""
"请注意，预填充节点和解码节点可能具有不同的配置。在此示例中，每个预填充节点独立部署为主节点，而解码节点使用 192.0.0.5 节点作为主节点。这会导致"
" 'dp_size_local' 和 'dp_rank_start' 的差异"

msgid "## Example proxy for Distributed DP Server"
msgstr "## 分布式 DP 服务器的示例代理"

msgid ""
"In the PD separation scenario, we need a proxy to distribute requests. "
"Execute the following commands to enable the example proxy:"
msgstr "在 PD 分离场景下，我们需要一个代理来分发请求。执行以下命令以启用示例代理："

msgid ""
"|Parameter  | meaning |\n"
"| --- | --- |\n"
"| --port | Proxy service Port |\n"
"| --host | Proxy service Host IP|\n"
"| --prefiller-hosts | Hosts of prefiller nodes |\n"
"| --prefiller-hosts-num | Number of repetitions for prefiller node hosts |\n"
"| --prefiller-ports | Ports of prefiller nodes |\n"
"| --prefiller-ports-inc | Number of increments for prefiller node ports |\n"
"| --decoder-hosts | Hosts of decoder nodes |\n"
"| --decoder-hosts-num | Number of repetitions for decoder node hosts |\n"
"| --decoder-ports | Ports of decoder nodes |\n"
"| --decoder-ports-inc | Number of increments for decoder node ports |"
msgstr ""
"|参数  | 含义 |\n"
"| --- | --- |\n"
"| --port | 代理服务端口 |\n"
"| --host | 代理服务主机 IP|\n"
"| --prefiller-hosts | 预填充节点的主机 |\n"
"| --prefiller-hosts-num | 预填充节点主机的重复次数 |\n"
"| --prefiller-ports | 预填充节点的端口 |\n"
"| --prefiller-ports-inc | 预填充节点端口的增量数 |\n"
"| --decoder-hosts | 解码节点的主机 |\n"
"| --decoder-hosts-num | 解码节点主机的重复次数 |\n"
"| --decoder-ports | 解码节点的端口 |\n"
"| --decoder-ports-inc | 解码节点端口的增量数 |"

msgid ""
"You can get the proxy program in the repository's examples, "
"[load\\_balance\\_proxy\\_server\\_example.py](https://github.com/vllm-"
"project/vllm-"
"ascend/blob/v0.9.1-dev/examples/disaggregate_prefill_v1/load_balance_proxy_server_example.py)"
msgstr ""
"您可以在仓库的示例中获取代理程序，[load\\_balance\\_proxy\\_server\\_example.py](https://github.com/vllm-"
"project/vllm-"
"ascend/blob/v0.9.1-dev/examples/disaggregate_prefill_v1/load_balance_proxy_server_example.py)"

